videos.description: Florida's Devin Robinson gets the block that leads to a Kevarrius Hayes dunk off a great pass from KeVaughn Allen.
videos.headline: Hayes with the strong dunk for the Gators

videos.description: ESPN commentator Sean Farnham drains a half-court shot and then impresses with another shot from way up in the seats.
videos.headline: Sean Farnham hits shot from the seats

videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes blocks Arkansas's Anton Beard in transition.
videos.headline: Hayes with the fantastic chase-down block

videos.description: Florida football head coach Jim McElwain is treated with a Peanut Butter and Jelly sandwich from the Gator for his 55th birthday.
videos.headline: Florida celebrates Football head coach's birthday

videos.description: Florida's Devin Robinson helps to extend the Gators' lead with an open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Robinson pads lead with 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida's Canyon Barry blocks Arkansas's Dustin Thomas.
videos.headline: Barry stifles Arkansas under the rim

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza fakes out the defender to hit the jumper to seal the game for the Gators.
videos.headline: Chiozza gets fancy with the jumper to secure victory

videos.description: Canyon Barry puts up 14 points and KeVaughn Allen adds 12 to boost the Gators to a victory over the Razorbacks.
videos.headline: No. 12 Florida outshoots Arkansas 78-65
